sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: VR
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Reverse primer for sequencing/amplifying BioBrick parts (VR)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Originally named VR, This reverse primer binds downstream of the standard BBa_MSC on biobrick vectors. Used for general-purpose PCR and sequencing of Biobrick parts.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Tom Knight

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: VF2
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Forward primer for sequencing/amplifying BioBrick parts (VF2)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Originally named VF2, primer binds upstream of the standard BBa_MCS on biobrick vectors.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Tom Knight

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_G00700
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Target sequence located approximately 400bp from the left end of pBAD. Suitable to sequence the final 800bp of pBAD
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Barry Canton

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BioBrick-f
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Forward BioBrick prefix primer for amplifying BioBrick parts (BioBrick-f)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Forward primer that binds to the BioBrick prefix. It is useful for amplifying BioBrick parts.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: It includes extra bases on the 5' end to enable both efficient cutting by EcoRI and 3' A addition by Taq polymerase.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Reshma Shetty

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BioBrick-r
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Reverse BioBrick suffix primer for amplifying BioBrick parts (BioBrick-r)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Reverse primer that binds to the BioBrick suffix. It is useful for amplifying BioBrick parts.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: It includes extra bases on the 5' end to enable both efficient cutting by EcoRI and 3' A addition by Taq polymerase.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Reshma Shetty

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_G00701
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Target sequence located approximately 400bp from the right end of I0500. Suitable for sequencing the first 800bp of pBAD
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Barry Canton
